    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Items related to Tool management are displayed on the Tool Data Screen.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;">To navigate to Tool Data Screen, press <text style="font-weight:bold;">[MENU]</text> <text styleclass style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text> press Makino icon <text styleclass style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text> Main Menu Screen is displayed <text styleclass style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text> press Tool Data Screen icon <text styleclass style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text> Tool Data Screen is displayed.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Tool details can be viewed in Detail mode or List mode. To toggle between Detail and List mode, press <text style="font-weight:bold;">[DETAIL]</text> / <text style="font-weight:bold;">[LIST]</text> soft key.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <list id="1" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="·" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px; font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;"> In Detail mode, individual tools information is displayed.</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"> In List mode, multiple tools data items are displayed in table form.</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">To change data values, press <text style="font-weight:bold;">[INPUT]</text> soft key.</para>
